557
00:33:03,445 --> 00:33:04,850
De acuerdo.

558
00:33:05,197 --> 00:33:07,210
Vale, Lombardi, ve con él.

559
00:33:08,450 --> 00:33:10,130
A la orden, jefe.

560
00:33:12,121 --> 00:33:14,130
